<br>
I asked several horsie people the other day and they said you DO still regen mana while running on the horse as if you are medding, but you won't with attack turned on. The mana regen is the same on any horse, its the same as medding sitting down. Before I was only going to buy one of my twinks a horse, but since you regen mana while running on it now my druid is thinking about it unless they &quot;fix&quot; that also.<br>
